            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Horst, I'm very sorry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "There's no need to apologize, it was a difficult request."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Also, this was originally caused by my own mistake. This isn't your fault alone, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It also seemed that Monika wasn't happy about singing, so this may have been the best outcome."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x52,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "So what happened with the concert?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I had Tess sing instead."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Huh, that sounds like it would be exciting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "No, as you said, it was exciting, in a way. Tess had a lot of fun. However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "However...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Her singing was very... Unique. Her choice of tone and pitch was... Different..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I-I see... That's unexpected..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Well, it was exciting, in its own way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "However, it would be most helpful if you could meet the deadlines from now on. Before Tess volunteers to sing again..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "O-okay..."
        }
    ]
